    "description": "《STILL WAKES THE DEEP》是创作方The Chinese Room的第一人称叙事恐怖类游戏回归之作，该工作室曾出品过众多备受赞誉的游戏，包括：《Amnesia: A Machine for Pigs》、《Everybody’s Gone to the Rapture》和《Dear Esther》。<br><br>你将扮演一名离岸石油钻井工人，必须穿越邪恶的风暴、危机四伏的环境以及黑暗、冰寒的北海水域，为自己的生命而战。所有通讯线路都被切断。 所有出口都无影无踪。剩下的只有直面那呼啸而来的未知恐惧。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1622910/extras/51aee519736638591bd054865b4c7844.poster.avif?t=1766147641\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1622910/extras/51aee519736638591bd054865b4c7844.webm?t=1766147641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1622910/extras/51aee519736638591bd054865b4c7844.mp4?t=1766147641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>身临其境地探索20世纪70年代苏格兰的一座海上石油钻井平台，整个故事过程中，这个平台会不断发生演变<br></li><li>世界级的视听与配文，由屡获殊荣的工作室The Chinese Room全情创作<br></li><li>明星云集的配音演员阵容，包括Alec Newman、Neve McIntosh等一众大伽<br></li><li>由Jason Graves带来的世界一流配乐，堪称余音绕梁<br></li><li>长达6小时的惊悚游戏过程<br></li><li>准备迎接一场充满惊险、恐惧与敬畏的交响乐</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1622910/extras/0ce6c103402c1ea134aa2d29c328f309.poster.avif?t=1766147641\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1622910/extras/0ce6c103402c1ea134aa2d29c328f309.webm?t=1766147641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1622910/extras/0ce6c103402c1ea134aa2d29c328f309.mp4?t=1766147641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >亲历恐怖</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>一段沉浸式的灾难故事，就发生在一个真实的北海石油钻井平台上<br></li><li>勇敢面对一个令人心悸、冷酷无情的敌人<br></li><li>诚心祈祷终有一天还能再次见到家人<br></li><li>当海水撕开人类迄今最坚固的结构体，同时也摧毁坚定无比的船员心志时，玩家将会对大海的绝美与残暴感同身受</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1622910/extras/3d565fb73ab301a0aed5035c4dc2a119.poster.avif?t=1766147641\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1622910/extras/3d565fb73ab301a0aed5035c4dc2a119.webm?t=1766147641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1622910/extras/3d565fb73ab301a0aed5035c4dc2a119.mp4?t=1766147641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >逃离钻井</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>躲避、干扰、潜行，拼尽全力求得生存<br></li><li>没有武器。没有技能。有的只是你的智慧和决心<br></li><li>在被海水淹没的廊道和暴雨肆虐的外甲板上奔跑、攀爬和游泳<br></li><li>为了生存而奋战，一旦走错一步，便有可能万劫不复</li></ul>",
